face was over&s;hadowed by this tremen|dous
nozzle; and the rueful eagerne&s;s
<PB N="33" REF="46">
with which he explained this unlucky
accident, was ludicrous beyond all de|&s;cription.
&mdash;I was much plea&s;ed with
meeting the original of a character, which
you and I have often laughed at in de|&s;cription;
and what &s;urprizes me very
much, I find the features in the picture,
